- if plan.focus_areas.empty?
  .status
    = image_tag 'attention.png', size: '32x32'
    Tips: Add a focus area so you know what to focus on.
    -#= link_to 'Add focus area', new_plan_focus_area_path(plan)
- elsif plan.tasks.empty?
  .status
    = image_tag 'attention.png', size: '32x32'
    Tips: Add tasks to focus areas so you can start taking actions.
    -#= link_to 'Add tasks', plan_path(plan)

- if plan.tasks.present? && (last_achievement = plan.last_achievement) && last_achievement.achieved_date < 2.weeks.ago
  .status
    = image_tag 'attention.png', size: '32x32'
    Tips: No action is recorded for this goal for more than two weeks.
    Taking an action is never a matter of ability but a matter of motivation.
    Review your goal.  Is it the 'Why' is not big enough?  Add more reasons why you want to achieve this goal.
